JOHANNESBURG - EFC 68 takes place in Cape Town on the 31 March with a tantalising main card of pure combat action. The Clinch spoke to EFC fighters and crew backstage at EFC 67 to get their main card predictions. In this final episode, they make their picks for the lightweight title fight between Martin 'The Punisher' van Staden (25-10) and Gavin 'Big Tasty' Hughes (9-0) eNCA